109
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,000
Aunt Lan

110
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,640
If your daughter is like you

111
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,200
and can't remember anything,

112
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:03,040
then I'll have to tell her about the past.

113
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,040
Don't push me.

114
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,600
I'm capable of anything.

115
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,640
It's none of your business.

116
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:20,000
You've made a mess of everything.

117
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,360
I really can't feel at ease.

118
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,080
You don't need to worry about it.

119
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,560
Useless coward.

120
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,480
Please leave my house.

121
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,000
