Captain Qin.

127
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,600
Gu Nan is here.

128
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,720
He says he has information about the crime scene to report.

129
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,480
Let's go.

130
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,200
August 1st.

131
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,440
Did you go to Shuntu Auto Repair Shop?

132
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,640
That was several days ago.

133
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,640
I don't really remember.

134
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,760
What, is fixing a car a crime now?

135
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,200
What time did you go?

136
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,600
What time did you leave the scene?

137
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,480
A little after eight, I think.

138
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,480
I left right after I finished the maintenance.

139
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,440
Did you know Zhang Xiaochuan is dead?

140
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,040
I saw it on the news.

141
00:08:34,800 --> 00:08:37,240
You left Wucheng on the 2nd. Where did you go?

142
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,680
My mom wasn't feeling well.

143
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:41,920
So I went home to check on her.

144
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,720
But I knew you were looking for me.

145
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,240
That's why I came over right away.

146
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,000
As far as we know,

147
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:54,360
you go to Shuntu Auto Repair Shop every week.

148
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:57,720
What kind of car needs maintenance every week?

149
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,600
What was your relationship with Zhang Xiaochuan?

150
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,480
Oh, that's what you're asking about?

151
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:09,000
Yes, it's exactly the kind of relationship you're thinking of.

152
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,120
Don't laugh.

153
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,560
Just answer the question.

154
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,680
I did answer.

155
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:18,040
Officer Qin, do you have to be so harsh?

156
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,160
I came here just to tell you

157
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:22,680
I really don't know how Zhang Xiaochuan died.

158
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,360
I didn't see anything.

159
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,240
He was fine when I left.

160
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,240
Was there a third person at the repair shop that day?

161
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,160
No.

162
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,280
Is that all?

163
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,160
Recently, some parents have raised concerns.

164
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,160
During the observation of the choir class,

165
00:09:58,160 --> 00:10:00,280
your performance in class was not good.

166
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:03,960
Why aren't you saying anything?

167
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,160
I'll pay attention.

168
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,080
Our cultural center

169
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,960
is now actively transitioning towards commercialization.

170
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:14,040
Look at all the different classes out there nowadays.

171
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,160
They're not big in scale,

172
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,040
but they have plenty of students.

173
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:16,720
And they charge high fees.

174
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,600
It's tough for me too.

175
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,480
If your class

176
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,040
has fewer than eight students,

177
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,720
I think we shouldn't run it.

178
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:29,200
The fees collected aren't even enough to cover the electricity bill.

179
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,160
What happened to your hand?

180
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:37,400
It's nothing, it'll be fine tomorrow.

181
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,720
If it's nothing, come here.

182
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,360
Play something for me.

183
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,360
Come on.

184
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,400
Play a piece.

185
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,160
How about this instead?

186
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,040
Let's play together.

187
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,960
You use one hand, I'll use the other.

188
00:10:59,160 --> 00:10:59,960
I'll coordinate with you.

189
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,040
How about it?

190
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:17,920
Look at you.

191
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,160
You're really careless.

192
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,280
The performance is coming up soon.

193
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,720
With your hand injured,

194
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,480
