195
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,080
Are you saying

196
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:32,160
I should go on stage with you?

197
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:55,400
Honey, I'm on my way home.

198
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:58,520
Tell Xiaobao that Daddy will be home soon.

199
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,400
Get up.

200
