You put up with everything all day long.

207
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,080
Who feels sorry for you?

208
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:11,960
Li Yan.

209
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,920
You have to learn to grow up on your own.

210
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,800
You have to protect yourself.

211
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:25,040
Do you understand?

212
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:32,960
It's okay now.

213
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,600
Captain Qin, you didn't go home last night?

214
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:00,280
I'll open the window for you.

215
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,160
What's wrong?

216
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,400
Come here first, you—

217
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,040
Help me, help me—

218
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,280
Put the medicated patch on for me, come on.

219
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,720
Be gentle.

220
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:13,840
Sorry, sorry.

221
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:15,800
Seriously.

222
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:18,720
Captain Qin.

223
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,840
