224
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:21,840
The details of the case.

225
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,360
Can you listen and see if I got it right?

226
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,720
Okay, go ahead.

227
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:25,600
So, Gu Nan—

228
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,960
