245
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:57,040
And Lin Yi totally seems like

246
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,600
someone with a huge ego,

247
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,920
maybe even

248
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,520
a bit of a pathological type.

249
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:03,720
Not bad.

250
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,160
You're making progress.

251
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,400
But Lin Yi has an alibi.

252
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,400
So...

253
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,400
