257
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,160
Let me tell you,

258
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,800
you can't learn just by being taught by others.

259
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:26,840
Experience is the best teacher—once is enough.

260
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:28,600
Captain Qin, what's up?

261
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,400
There's a case from the traffic police.

262
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:32,160
They want us to take a look.

263
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,400
What's going on?

264
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:35,960
Aunt Lan.

265
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,000
Long time no see.
